title: Automated Kovarex Enrichment Process
descriptionMarkdown:
Tilable Kovarex Enrichment Build, which uses a cuircuit network to not overfill.

Research requirements:
   - `Logistic system`
   - `Inserter capacity bonus` `1`

Place as many instances as you wish next to each other. Make sure the bufferchests overlap.
Replace the first bufferchest with a requester- and the last buffer chest with a passive provider chest.

Each instance has to be kickstarted by hand by placing the first 40 + 5 uranium ores inside the Centrifuge.

As long the logistics network requests Uranium-235 (either by requester chest, or by player) and enough Uranium-238 is available in the buffer chest, 
the centrifuges will restart their enrichment cycle.
